<section id="Section519617">
  <title>
<indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>count tags</primary>

      <secondary>by item</secondary>
    </indexterm> <indexterm significance="normal">
      <primary>items</primary>

      <secondary>count tags for</secondary>
    </indexterm>Count Tags by Item</title>

  <para>To view a display of Count Tags by Item, select the "Count Tags by
  Item" option. The following screen will appear:</para>

  <para>
<screenshot>
      <mediaobject>
        <imageobject>
          <imagedata fileref="images/dspCountTagsByItem.png"/>
        </imageobject>

        <caption>Count Tags by Item</caption>
      </mediaobject>
    </screenshot>
</para>

  <para>When displaying Count Tags by Item, you are presented with the
  following options:</para>

  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>Item Number</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Enter the Item Number of the Item Count Tags you want to
        view.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>UOM</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Inventory Unit of Measure.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry role="openmfg">
      <term>All Warehouses</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Select to display Count Tags for all Warehouses.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry role="openmfg">
      <term>Selected</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Specify Warehouse whose Count Tags you want to display.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>Start Date</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Count Tags entered on and after this date will be
        displayed.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>End Date</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Count Tags entered on and before this date will be
        displayed.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>Show Unposted Count Tags</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Select to display unposted Count Tags.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>Count Tags</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Display lists Count Tags by Item, using the specified
        parameters.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>

  <para>To the far right of the screen, the following buttons are
  available:</para>

  <variablelist>
    <varlistentry>
      <term>CLOSE</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Closes the screen, returning you to the application
        desktop.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>QUERY</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Select to generate the display, using the specified
        parameters.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

    <varlistentry>
      <term>PRINT</term>

      <listitem>
        <para>Runs the report associated with this screen.</para>
      </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
  </variablelist>

  <para>Right-clicking on a Count Tag in the Count Tags list enables you to
  select the following menu options:</para>

  <variablelist>
    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../supportfiles/rightclick.xml" xpointer="element(/1/8/2/28)"/>

    <xi:include xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude" href="../widgets/xtreewidget.xml" xpointer="element(xtreewidget.menu.exportcontents)"/>
  </variablelist>
</section>
